-- Tanzania's Ruling Party Names Shein as Zanzibar Presidential Candidate
-- Wilfred Mwakalosi
-- 2010-07-10T09:19:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-10/tanzania-s-ruling-party-names-shein-as-zanzibar-presidential-candidate.html

          
          
             Tanzaniaâ€™s ruling Chama Cha
Mapinduzi party chose vice president  Ali Mohamed Shein  as its
candidate for the Zanzibar presidency in general elections to be
held in October.  
 President  Jakaya Kikwete  announced the candidacy on state
television, Tanzania Broadcast Corp. Shein will compete for the
position as head of the semi-autonomous archipelago against  Seif Sharrif Hamad  from the opposition Civic United Front.  
